<i>Nu-i niciun mister.</i>

508
00:35:14,902 --> 00:35:19,439
<i>Spectacolul e plin de caracter.</i>

509
00:35:19,474 --> 00:35:23,904
<i>Şi nu e deloc auster.</i>

510
00:35:23,939 --> 00:35:28,503
