524
00:36:08,334 --> 00:36:12,792
<i>Da, vino!
Vino, vino, vino!</i>

525
00:36:12,827 --> 00:36:14,692
<i>Te simţi mai bine?</i>

526
00:36:14,727 --> 00:36:16,247
