a venit domnul Contini.

555
00:39:19,323 --> 00:39:23,409
Îmi place Charlie Chaplin.

556
00:39:23,444 --> 00:39:25,476
Şi mie.

557
00:39:25,511 --> 00:39:27,509
Un geniu.

558
00:39:28,170 --> 00:39:32,351
