566
00:39:55,386 --> 00:40:00,052
- Străduieşte-te mai mult.
- Da, aşa voi face.

567
00:40:00,087 --> 00:40:04,453
Eminenţa voastră...

568
00:40:04,704 --> 00:40:07,015
