626
00:47:28,854 --> 00:47:31,088
Adu-l aici.

627
00:47:31,123 --> 00:47:35,328
Acest sălbatic e diavolul.

628
00:47:35,363 --> 00:47:41,264
Dumnezeu te va pedepsi
pentru păcatele tale, acum şi pururea.

629
00:47:54,251 --> 00:47:55,351
